# Safe Refactor Skill

## Goal
Improve code structure without changing behavior.

## Preconditions
- All tests must be passing

## Steps

1. Run full test suite
2. Identify duplication or complexity
3. Refactor smallest safe section
4. Re-run tests after each change
5. Ensure no behavior changes occurred

## Rules
- No refactor if tests are failing
- No feature changes during refactor
- Small incremental edits only

## Output
- Cleaner structure
- Same behavior
- Passing tests